00:32:56.191 --> 00:32:58.690
Actually, it was probably the
only day of summer in Ireland.

00:32:58.690 --> 00:33:00.560
And the weather was fantastic.

00:33:00.560 --> 00:33:04.020
We volunteered, kids,
bouncy castles, great fun.

00:33:04.020 --> 00:33:05.770
And [INAUDIBLE] from
the [INAUDIBLE] team,

00:33:05.770 --> 00:33:07.460
she may be here, she
might not be here--

00:33:07.460 --> 00:33:08.320
oh, there you are.

00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:12.260
[INAUDIBLE] is running the
