00:33:48.860 --> 00:33:50.150
It's not a chore.

00:33:50.150 --> 00:33:52.140
It's just part of what we do.

00:33:52.140 --> 00:33:53.410
It's not an agenda.

00:33:53.410 --> 00:33:55.660
And by the way, if you want
