rubbish 20 years ago,

00:58:23.788 --> 00:58:25.710
and how you've made that
change, to pretending

00:58:25.710 --> 00:58:27.000
that you've got
something to patronize

00:58:27.000 --> 00:58:28.041
these black people about.

00:58:28.041 --> 00:58:30.870
So it's kind of really
understanding our role in that,

00:58:30.870 --> 00:58:32.192
I think.

